data.description: Welcome to one of the most desirable multi-family homes in Stow! This immaculate duplex has been meticulously maintained and is ready for the next owner. This home is an incredible investment opportunity that cash flows beautifully. Each unit is rented for $1200 monthly, and tenants pay for all the utilities except water. You could also have a tenant pay your mortgage or convert to an in-law suite.  Each unit offers two separate living areas, a laundry/utility room, two bedrooms, 1.5 baths and spacious eat-in kitchen. Each unit also has its own garage. This one won't last! Schedule your showing today!
